1
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 13=
(The Trash's True Colors)

3
00:01:22,079 --> 00:01:24,079
Finally, we took down the trash.

4
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:24,719
Come on.

5
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:25,640
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

6
00:01:31,439 --> 00:01:31,879
Oh yeah.

7
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:37,400
This is what I got from He Jinchen.

8
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:38,799
Turns out he wanted

9
00:01:38,879 --> 00:01:40,959
to secretly move
all of Meiyan's shady departments

10
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:42,799
to the resort.

11
00:01:43,359 --> 00:01:44,840
How insidious.

12
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:48,799
So his acquisition under Shengda's name

13
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,079
was just a cover.

14
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:52,920
There is no way I'm letting him
get away with it.

15
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:55,640
He is not taking the resort from me.

16
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:05,799
Ms. Su,

17
00:02:06,719 --> 00:02:08,080
are we only allowed to talk about work

18
00:02:08,599 --> 00:02:09,520
every time we go out?

19
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,400
Then what do you want to talk about?

20
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,960
Our next move

21
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,599
should be to turn the He brothers

22
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:36,520
against each other.

23
00:02:37,319 --> 00:02:38,039
Then,

24
00:02:38,919 --> 00:02:40,759
while He Jinchen is distracted,

25
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,240
our people can slip in.

26
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,360
Aren't you talking about work too?

27
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,560
My heel! My heel!

28
00:03:23,719 --> 00:03:24,439
I'll buy you new ones.

29
00:03:24,479 --> 00:03:25,560
Put me down!

30
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:26,879
My heel!

31
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,680
My heel!

32
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,520
My heel!

33
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,199
Niannian!

34
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:36,199
Let me explain, Niannian!

35
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:37,520
Someone set me up that day.

36
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:38,759
They tried to ruin our marriage.

37
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:39,960
I didn't do anything with her!

38
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:40,680
I swear!

39
00:03:40,719 --> 00:03:41,439
Let go of me!

40
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,159
Niannian!

41
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,680
I have already transferred all the money

42
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:46,080
into your account.

43
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:47,879
My money is your money.

44
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:50,199
You are my only one.

45
00:03:50,439 --> 00:03:51,719
Can't you trust me?

46
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:53,360
Really?

47
00:04:00,180 --> 00:04:02,060
(Credited 88 million yuan)

48
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:09,520
Dear,

49
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,400
even if it's not for me,

50
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,080
think about An'an.

51
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,639
He needs a complete family.

52
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:22,199
Dear, let's go home.

53
00:04:34,079 --> 00:04:34,639
Hold it.

54
00:04:37,439 --> 00:04:38,000
Come on, dear.

55
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,199
Let's go home.

56
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:43,199
Dear, you have no idea

57
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,079
while you were away,

58
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,480
I couldn't fall asleep at all.

59
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:46,519
I felt like

60
00:04:46,639 --> 00:04:47,800
slapping myself.

61
00:04:48,879 --> 00:04:49,439
Go ahead.

62
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:50,319
You do it too.

63
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,639
Your face might be fine,
but my hand is not.

64
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,480
Dear, I swear.

65
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:57,199
I swear.

66
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:58,639
From now on, we will

67
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,120
live happily forever.

68
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,399
I even made you some bird's nest soup.

69
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,160
Let me get it.

70
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:03,959
You rest for a bit.

71
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:20,399
Niannian, I love you.

72
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,040
I love you.

73
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:23,759
Come back.

74
00:05:23,879 --> 00:05:24,560
You fool.

75
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,959
As long as you come back,

76
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,680
I would die for you.

77
00:05:28,519 --> 00:05:29,600
He still loves me.

78
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,079
You can't drink this.

79
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:39,959
What are you doing?

80
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:41,079
What?

81
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:43,120
Now that your wife is back,
you forget about me?

82
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,439
Spending big money

83
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,199
on premium bird's nest for her,

84
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,680
and I cannot even have a sip?

85
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,839
Why are you so jealous?

86
00:05:51,319 --> 00:05:53,319
After I win back that lovesick fool

87
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,439
and get more money,

88
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,879
do you think I'd forget about you?

89
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,879
Now you see what he really is.

90
00:06:10,079 --> 00:06:12,199
But he gave me all the money.

91
00:06:12,519 --> 00:06:14,319
He even promised me
all his future earnings.

92
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:17,560
Why would he do that?

93
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,839
High investment
is always for high returns.

94
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,480
He's just using you for his own gain.

95
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:29,639
I hope you stay clear-headed.

96
00:06:30,879 --> 00:06:32,360
Then tell me

97
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,240
your decision.

98
00:06:44,319 --> 00:06:44,959
Niannian,

99
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:47,360
I made this bird's nest for you.

100
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,759
You've lost weight lately.

101
00:06:48,959 --> 00:06:49,839
You need to nourish yourself.

102
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:50,759
Here.

103
00:06:55,279 --> 00:06:56,480
Niannian, what is wrong?

104
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:57,600
Aren't you going to have some?

105
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:58,759
Here, let me feed you.

106
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:04,639
Here.

107
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:37,199
(No way it works that fast.)

108
00:07:52,319 --> 00:07:53,319
How did you know

109
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:55,279
about my husband and the maid?

110
00:07:58,279 --> 00:08:01,399
Once a cheater, always a cheater.

111
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,240
Pay a little attention
and you will notice.

112
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,600
Besides,

113
00:08:06,079 --> 00:08:08,079
He Jinchuan is a piece of trash.

114
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,399
You're just pretending you don't know.

115
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,519
So what if I know?

116
00:08:13,959 --> 00:08:16,160
Maybe this is how

117
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,639
arranged marriages end.

118
00:08:19,319 --> 00:08:20,120
I still have An'an.

119
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,600
To give An'an a complete family,

120
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,199
I can turn a blind eye.

121
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,199
My son

122
00:08:26,839 --> 00:08:27,920
must be happier than me.

123
00:08:29,279 --> 00:08:30,360
If the mother is not happy,

124
00:08:31,439 --> 00:08:32,600
how can the son be happy?

125
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:36,519
Besides, if you don't take actions now,

126
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:37,639
are you sure

127
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,639
An'an will have a complete family?

128
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,639
What do you mean by that?

129
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,840
Recently, have you been feeling

130
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,360
sleepy and weak,

131
00:08:47,919 --> 00:08:48,799
with heart palpitations, nausea,

132
00:08:49,159 --> 00:08:49,919
dizziness, and the urge to throw up?

133
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:55,000
Maybe I'm pregnant again.

134
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,000
I suggest

135
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,879
you check your daily diet instead.

136
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:03,080
There might be another issue.

137
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:07,679
(Here, dear.)

138
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:11,399
(Is it good?)

139
00:09:11,879 --> 00:09:12,679
(Here, have some more.)

140
00:09:14,799 --> 00:09:15,879
(Good girl.)

141
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:21,200
Get up!

142
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:26,759
Tian Gang.

143
00:09:27,879 --> 00:09:28,919
If you confess honestly

144
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,480
about your deal with Gu Qingmei,

145
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,080
I will let you go.

146
00:09:33,639 --> 00:09:34,360
What deal?

147
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:35,639
I... I...

148
00:09:36,039 --> 00:09:37,080
I don't understand.

149
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,000
(Recording)
Dad,

150
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,759
(Recording)
when are you coming home?

151
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,480
I miss you so much.

152
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,519
- Dad.
- Niannian!

153
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:51,960
What did you do to her?

154
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:55,159
Let me go! Let me go!

155
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:01,720
Niannian

156
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:04,039
is six years old.

157
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,919
She is quite adorable.

158
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,279
Don't hurt her!

159
00:10:08,639 --> 00:10:09,279
He Jinchen!

160
00:10:09,679 --> 00:10:10,840
If you've got a problem, come at me.

161
00:10:13,639 --> 00:10:15,559
Just tell me Gu Qingmei's secret,

162
00:10:16,279 --> 00:10:17,519
and I will let you go immediately.

163
00:10:18,039 --> 00:10:19,480
I will even give you a sum of money.

164
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,000
That way,

165
00:10:21,679 --> 00:10:23,159
you and your daughter

166
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:25,519
will never have to
live this hard life again.

167
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:29,919
Alright.

168
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:31,840
I will tell you.

169
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,320
But don't hurt my daughter.

170
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:38,360
She...

171
00:10:39,039 --> 00:10:40,480
She is not Gu Qingmei.

172
00:10:42,919 --> 00:10:44,000
Her name is Su Li.

173
00:10:54,399 --> 00:10:55,480
Have you found Tian Gang?

174
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,200
Not yet.

175
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:57,840
I suspect he fled the city

176
00:10:57,879 --> 00:10:58,919
out of fear of being implicated.

177
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,919
Check his relatives.

178
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,519
See if anyone
has contacted him recently.

179
00:11:04,919 --> 00:11:05,360
Alright.

180
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:06,200
Besides,

181
00:11:06,919 --> 00:11:07,639
notify Ms. Wang

182
00:11:08,879 --> 00:11:09,840
to keep an eye on Su Li at all times.

183
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,399
If anything happens,

184
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:12,480
let me know immediately.

185
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,639
What could possibly happen?

186
00:11:15,799 --> 00:11:16,279
Alright.

187
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:18,519
I will keep her safe at all times.

188
00:11:18,759 --> 00:11:20,519
No mistakes, guaranteed.

189
00:11:21,759 --> 00:11:22,399
Mr. He,

190
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,600
I will tell you everything.

191
00:11:25,039 --> 00:11:25,840
Her name is Su Li.

192
00:11:26,159 --> 00:11:27,240
She is a journalist.

193
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,279
I had given her

194
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:29,799
some dirt on Meiyan before.

195
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:30,919
But that whole story

196
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:33,039
was something I made up
to get back at Meiyan.

197
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,879
Then why did she come to you recently?

198
00:11:37,519 --> 00:11:38,120
She...

199
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:40,440
She said she lost her memories.

200
00:11:41,159 --> 00:11:41,720
She said

201
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,639
she had seen me before.

202
00:11:44,879 --> 00:11:45,559
Mr. He,

203
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,279
I have told you everything.

204
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,639
Please let me go.

205
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:49,440
Mr. He!

206
00:11:55,799 --> 00:11:57,480
Get out of Rong City right now.

207
00:11:57,759 --> 00:11:58,879
Don't let anyone see you.

208
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,159
Otherwise,

209
00:12:00,519 --> 00:12:02,039
I have ways

210
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:05,320
to make your life a living hell.

211
00:12:07,519 --> 00:12:08,360
(Miss Su.)

212
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:09,720
(I'm sorry.)

213
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:14,639
Go.

214
00:12:22,639 --> 00:12:24,440
So you are not Gu Qingmei.

215
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:27,000
Did you really lose your memory,

216
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:30,120
or is this all part of some plan?

217
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:40,639
Qingmei.

218
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:44,120
I picked this out for you.

219
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:47,240
Do you like it?

220
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,080
Yes.

221
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:51,879
(Indeed different from Gu Qingmei.)

222
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:53,720
(You don't like jewelry.)

223
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,480
You used to love jewelry.

224
00:12:57,679 --> 00:12:58,399
Every time you received one,

225
00:12:58,639 --> 00:13:00,120
you could not wait to put it on.

226
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,200
(He suddenly brings up the past.)

227
00:13:03,159 --> 00:13:04,320
(He knows I'm not Gu Qingmei.)

228
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,320
(He is testing me.)

229
00:13:09,759 --> 00:13:11,480
Why? You don't like it anymore?

230
00:13:12,799 --> 00:13:14,720
Maybe the old me did like it.

231
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:17,159
But since I lost my memories,

232
00:13:17,759 --> 00:13:18,639
my heart tells me

233
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:19,879
to be a career woman.

234
00:13:20,159 --> 00:13:21,799
So, these jewelry pieces

235
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,399
don't interest me anymore.

236
00:13:24,759 --> 00:13:25,879
Can a person's personality change

237
00:13:26,159 --> 00:13:27,679
that much after losing memories?

238
00:13:27,919 --> 00:13:28,559
Really?

239
00:13:30,519 --> 00:13:31,399
I don't know.

240
00:13:32,279 --> 00:13:33,720
The harder I try to remember,

241
00:13:33,799 --> 00:13:34,919
the more it slips away.

242
00:13:35,519 --> 00:13:36,360
If I try to recall too much,

243
00:13:36,799 --> 00:13:37,799
my head hurts.

244
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:42,039
(Since you have not regained
your memory,)

245
00:13:42,799 --> 00:13:44,840
(it is best you never remember.)

246
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:48,799
Are you sleeping here tonight?

247
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,399
This is our room.

248
00:13:51,559 --> 00:13:52,799
We are married.

249
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:54,039
What are you doing?

250
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:56,039
What do you want at midnight?

251
00:13:56,799 --> 00:13:58,320
The midnight is just perfect

252
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,159
for us to...

253
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:08,020
(Mu Shaoze)

254
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,240
Mu Shaoze's call.

255
00:14:14,879 --> 00:14:15,679
Aren't you going to pick up?

256
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:18,039
Nothing important.

257
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,279
Focus on being Mrs. He.

258
00:14:26,279 --> 00:14:28,440
The career woman life is not for you.

259
00:15:00,900 --> 00:15:05,660
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

260
00:15:05,660 --> 00:15:10,500
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

261
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:15,060
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

262
00:15:15,060 --> 00:15:19,980
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

263
00:15:19,980 --> 00:15:23,780
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

264
00:15:23,780 --> 00:15:28,580
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

265
00:15:28,580 --> 00:15:31,420
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

266
00:15:31,420 --> 00:15:34,100
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

267
00:15:34,460 --> 00:15:40,020
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

268
00:15:40,420 --> 00:15:47,220
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

269
00:15:47,500 --> 00:15:52,180
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

270
00:15:52,340 --> 00:15:59,140
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

271
00:15:59,460 --> 00:16:06,260
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

272
00:16:06,460 --> 00:16:10,940
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

273
00:16:10,940 --> 00:16:14,300
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

274
00:16:14,300 --> 00:16:21,220
♪Right as I confess my love♪
